- <section>
- <aside class="notes"> Notes
- <section> inside <section> creates vertical sides
- <section data-markdown>
	<script type="text/template">
  Markdown support
- <p class="fragment" data-fragment-index="1"> Fragment inside a section
- Fragment styles: grow, shrink, roll-in, fadeout, current-visible, highlight-blue, highlight-red
  <p class="fragment grow">
- transitions
- themes
- <section data-background="">
  + RGB
  + Img Link
  + data-background-repeat="repeat"
    * data-background-size="100px"
  + Video
    * data-background-video
- Transitions
  * <section data-transition="slide" data-background="#rrggbb" data-background-transition="zoom">
- Code
  * <pre><code style="word-wrap: break-word;">
  * <pre><code data-trim contenteditable>
- <UL>, <OL>, <TABLE>
- Quotes:
  1. Inline
     - <q cite="http://">&ldquo;....&rdquo;</q>
  2. block
     - <blockquote cite="http://">
- Internal side links
  + <a href="#/2/3">
- Keyboard shortcuts
  + S : Speaker View
  + Esc : Overview
  + B or . : Pause
- Global state
  + <section data-state="classname">
- pdf export
- Custom JS per slide
  + <section data-state="eventname.blah">
  + <script type="text/javascript">Reveal.addEventListener("eventname.blah", function() {})</script>
